{
  "texts": [
    "The facts have been automatically extracted from Wikipedia and unified with WordNet, using a combination of rule-based and heuristic methods.",
    "The resulting knowledge base represents an improved WordNet, by adding knowledge about individuals like persons, organisations, products, etc., with their semantic relationships.",
    "In its original version, YAGO contains more than 1 million entities (like persons, organisations, cities, etc.)",
    "and contains more than 5 million facts (was born, wrote music for, etc.)",
    "about these entities."
  ]
}